<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- فَإِنْ أَبَى <span class="c2">(١)</span> بِلَا عُذْرٍ: فُرِّقَ بَيْنَهُمَا بِطَلَبِهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ لَمْ يُعْلَمْ خَبَرُهُ:</span> فَلَا فَسْخَ لِذَلِكَ بِحَالٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَحَرُمَ جَمْعُ زَوْجَتَيْهِ بِمَسْكَنٍ وَاحِدٍ مَا لَمْ يَرْضَيَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَلَهُ مَنْعُهَا مِنَ الخُرُوجِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَعَلَى غَيْرِ طِفْلٍ:</span> التَّسْوِيَةُ بَيْنَ زَوْجَاتٍ فِي القَسْمِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- لَا فِي وَطْءٍ، وَكِسْوَةٍ، وَنَحْوِهِمَا إِذَا قَامَ بِالوَاجِبِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَعِمَادُهُ:</span> اللَّيْلُ،<span class="c5"> إِلَّا فِي حَارِسٍ وَنَحْوِهِ:</span> فَالنَّهَارُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَزَوْجَةٌ أَمَةٌ عَلَى النِّصْفِ مِنْ حُرَّةٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَمُبَعَّضَةٌ بِالحِسَابِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- أَبَتِ المَبِيتَ مَعَهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- أَوِ السَّفَرَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- أَوْ سَافَرَتْ فِي حَاجَتِهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (د): كان. مكان قوله: (أبى).</p> </div>